From: Hannes Reinecke <hare@suse.de>
Date: Tue, 2 Jun 2020 13:09:51 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] dm zoned: move random and sequential zones into struct
Git-commit: bd82fdabf162fec1404c4e22988b178c4f3dd23b
